 Contact Us 





 



Scotiabank, through our Global Banking and Markets division,  provides corporate and investment banking and capital markets products and  services to corporate, institutional and government clients around the globe.  We have over 30 offices globally and more than 300 relationship managers  organized around industry specialties.  
If you have  questions or require information on our products and services, please contact us.

Please note your email is submitted through an unsecure site, therefore refrain from including confidential information
      (eg. your account #(s), credit card numbers and other personal information) in your e-mail.
If you are interested in applying for an employment opportunity, please visit our Careers website.
