Latin America and the Caribbean

Bahamas

Scotiabank has a local office in  Nassau Bahamas and offers offshore booking for Derivative and Global Fixed  Income products. Through our Global Banking and Markets division, we can also  provide clients with access to other corporate and investment banking and  capital markets products and services. In addition, we offer a range of Cash  Management and Trade Finance services through other areas of Scotiabank.




      



      For more information, please visit our local Bahamas website. 


