Precious and Base Metals 
Structured Products 


Global Transaction  Banking (Trade Finance and Correspondent Banking Services)

Commodity Trade Finance Services 
Correspondent Banking Services (International and local  Financial Institutions) 
Documentary Collections 
Import and Export Financing 
Import and Export LCs (advising, negotiation, confirmation,  etc.) 
Stand By LCs 


Clients also have access to  the Scotiabank network in over 50 countries, including Asia, USA, Canada,  Caribbean countries and Latin America (i.e. Brazil, Chile, Peru, Colombia,  Mexico, Costa Rica, Dominican Republic, El Salvador, Guatemala, Panama, Puerto  Rico and Uruguay among others).




    



