China
Scotiabank has been in China for more than 30 years with offices located in major markets throughout the country.  We have a representative office in Beijing and branches in Shanghai, Guangzhou and Chongqing.  These branches can service client needs throughout the country with foreign and local currency financing solutions, strong local market knowledge, and service in Chinese and English.




In China, we also provide clients with precious and base metal products through ScotiaMocatta, and oil and gas advisory through Scotia Waterous.




In addition, clients have access to a range of Cash Management and Trade Finance services.

