India

Scotiabank is proud to  maintain a strong presence in India with 3 branches in Mumbai, New Delhi and Bangalore. In India, we offer a range of corporate  services in trade finance, loans, deposits, cash management, foreign exchange,  precious and base metals products and services. ScotiaMocatta, the precious and  base metals business line of Scotiabank, has been recognized as the Best  Bullion Bank for five years in a row (2009-2013) by the Bombay Bullion  Association (BBA), a major center for gold and silver trading in India and  continues to be a leader in metals trading and financing in the region.




  Through other areas  of Scotiabank, we also offer clients a range of Cash Management and Trade  Finance services.


