Japan

Scotiabank has been serving clients in Japan since  1962. We offer a range of corporate loan and investment services, as well as  Cash Management and Trade Finance from offshore. Scotia Securities Asia Limited Tokyo Branch provides  Fixed Income, Equity Advisory, Foreign Exchange and Commodity solutions to its  clients by leveraging our broad geographic reach and extensive sectoral  expertise.
For more information, please visit our local Japan website.


