Scotiabank's Automotive Group 



		provides a full range of credit, capital markets and non-credit 



		services to corporations, financial sponsors and institutions 



		around the world. As part of the Bank's strategy, we have 



		successfully built an industry specialization in automotive 



		and have served North American markets for over 50 years.
Globalization of the automotive industry requires creative 



          financing alternatives with a bank that has specific industry



          knowledge and a global focus. Scotiabank has a group



          of  dedicated industry specialists in  North America,  



          Europe and South America who  work together as a team to serve the needs of our clients.       
Scotiabank offers a variety of services geared toward the automotive industry 



          in North America, including: 

Corporate and Syndicated Lending
