Mexico
 Scotiabank offers full coverage for clients in the Automotive sector in Mexico. We have dedicated industry specialists with extensive experience in the sector, who have long-standing relationships with local clients and local subsidiaries of global corporations in Mexico.
Scotiabank's Mexico specialists work together with their counterparts in the USA, Canada and Europe as a team to manage local and global client relationships for automotive and trucking OEMs, suppliers, captive finance companies, car-rental companies, and mega-dealers.
Products and services include: 

Lending 
Debt and Equity Financing 
Mergers and Acquisitions 
Risk Management 
Asset Securitization 
Sales, Trading and Research 
Foreign Exchange 

In addition, through other Scotiabank areas we offer full access to cash and treasury management services, electronic banking, trade finance and correspondent banking.





