Scotiabank is a leading provider of private placements in Canada and the U.S. Private placements are also available in Mexico through our local Mergers and Acquisitions group in Mexico City.		
Scotiabank is a leading Canadian provider of financial advisory services for companies seeking to raise private equity. Scotiabank's Equity Private Placement Group serves clients targeting both venture capital and traditional private equity for management buyouts, growth/expansion financing, and re-capitalizations. Over the last 12 months Scotiabank has acted as advisor and agent in some of Canada's largest equity private placements. The group's ability to understand the client's business  and accurately value a company are the group's best-recognized strengths. 





